grade-to-pro&utm_content=field-visibility\";s:4:\"plan\";a:2:{i:0;s:4:\"plus\";i:1;s:12:\"professional\";}}i:8;O:8:\"stdClass\":7:{s:5:\"title\";s:16:\"Multi Step Forms\";s:4:\"slug\";s:28:\"user-registration-multi-part\";s:4:\"name\";s:28:\"User Registration Multi Part\";s:5:\"image\";s:46:\"extensions-json/sections/images/multi-part.png\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:315:\"Lengthy forms are time-consuming and boring. Form fillers easily get distracted and quit halfway through these types of forms. But, there’s no need to worry! Our User Registration Multi-Part Add-on allows you to divide your registration forms into multiple parts according to your requirements without any hassle.\";s:4:\"link\";s:146:\"https://wpuserregistration.com/features/multi-step/?utm_source=addons-page&utm_medium=banner&utm_campaign=ur-upgrade-to-pro&utm_content=multi-part\";s:4:\"plan\";a:2:{i:0;s:4:\"plus\";i:1;s:12:\"professional\";}}i:9;O:8:\"stdClass\":7:{s:5:\"title\";s:15:\"Profile Connect\";s:4:\"slug\";s:33:\"user-registration-profile-connect\";s:4:\"name\";s:33:\"User Registration Profile Connect\";s:5:\"image\";s:51:\"extensions-json/sections/images/profile-connect.png\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:211:\"Connect your old users i.e users created via some other plugins, default WordPress registration form to user registration forms. Allows both individual as well as bulk connection of users to any particular form.\";s:4:\"link\";s:156:\"https://wpuserregistration.com/features/profile-connect/?utm_source=addons-page&utm_medium=banner&utm_campaign=ur-upgrade-to-pro&utm_content=profile-connect\";s:4:\"plan\";a:2:{i:0;s:4:\"plus\";i:1;s:12:\"professional\";}}i:10;O:8:\"stdClass\":7:{s:5:\"title\";s:14:\"Social Connect\";s:4:\"slug\";s:32:\"user-registration-social-connect\";s:4:\"name\";s:34:\"User Registration - Social Connect\";s:5:\"image\";s:42:\"extensions-json/sections/images/social.png\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:242:\"Signing up made easier and faster! With this addon you can make your users register to your site with social platforms like Facebook, Twitter, Google+, LinkedIn or others. Users details will be automatically pulled from their social profiles.\";s:4:\"link\";s:154:\"https://wpuserregistration.com/features/social-connect/?utm_source=addons-page&utm_medium=banner&utm_campaign=ur-upgrade-to-pro&utm_content=social-connect\";s:4:\"plan\";a:3:{i:0;s:8:\"personal\";i:1;s:4:\"plus\";i:2;s:12:\"professional\";}}i:11;O:8:\"stdClass\":7:{s:5:\"title\";s:9:\"MailChimp\";s:4:\"slug\";s:27:\"user-registration-mailchimp\";s:4:\"name\";s:29:\"User Registration - Mailchimp\";s:5:\"image\";s:45:\"extensions-json/sections/images/mailchimp.png\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:203:\"MailChimp add-on of User Registration plugin synchronizes your mailChimp account with User Registration plugin and automatically subscribes your site users to your mailchimp mailing list on registration.\";s:4:\"link\";s:144:\"https://wpuserregistration.com/features/mailchimp/?utm_source=addons-page&utm_medium=banner&utm_campaign=ur-upgrade-to-pro&utm_content=mailchimp\";s:4:\"plan\";a:3:{i:0;s:8:\"personal\";i:1;s:4:\"plus\";i:2;s:12:\"professional\";}}i:12;O:8:\"stdClass\":7:{s:5:\"title\";s:15:\"Email Templates\";s:4:\"slug\";s:33:\"user-registration-email-templates\";s:4:\"name\";s:33:\"User Registration Email Templates\";s:5:\"image\";s:51:\"extensions-json/sections/images/email-templates.png\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:179:\"Allows you to choose an email template or create a custom email template. It offers an easy-to-use customizer for you to change the look and feel of your User Registration emails.\";s:4:\"link\";s:156:\"https://wpuserregistration.com/features/email-templates/?utm_source=addons-page&utm_medium=banner&utm_campaign=ur-upgrade-to-pro&utm_content=email-templates\";s:4:\"plan\";a:2:{i:0;s:4:\"plus\";i:1;s:12:\"professional\";}}i:13;O:8:\"stdClass\":7:{s:5:\"title\";s:12:\"Invite Codes\";s:4:\"slug\";s:30:\"user-registration-invite-codes\";s:4:\"name\";s:30:\"User Registration Invite Codes\";s:5:\"image\";s:48:\"extensions-json/sections/images/invite-codes.png\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:198:\" Allows you to restrict the registration on your site to users with invite Codes only. You can create a single or multiple invitation code, set expiry date, usage limit per invitation code and more.\";s:4:\"link\";s:150:\"https://wpuserregistration.com/features/invite-codes/?utm_source=addons-page&utm_medium=banner&utm_campaign=ur-upgrade-to-pro&utm_content=invite-codes\";s:4:\"plan\";a:2:{i:0;s:4:\"plus\";i:1;s:12:\"professional\";}}i:14;O:8:\"stdClass\":7:{s:5:\"title\";s:11:\"Geolocation\";s:4:\"slug\";s:29:\"user-registration-geolocation\";s:4:\"name\";s:29:\"User Registration Geolocation\";s:5:\"image\";s:47:\"extensions-json/sections/images/geolocation.png\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:187:\"Allows you to collect geo location data from users who registered on your site. Information like Country, City, Zip Code, Latitude/Longitude and location map for the user will accessible.\";s:4:\"link\";s:148:\"https://wpuserregistration.com/features/geolocation/?utm_source=addons-page&utm_medium=banner&utm_campaign=ur-upgrade-to-pro&utm_content=geolocation\";s:4:\"plan\";a:2:{i:0;s:4:\"plus\";i:1;s:12:\"professional\";}}i:15;O:8:\"stdClass\":7:{s:5:\"title\";s:19:\"PDF Form Submission\";s:4:\"slug\";s:37:\"user-registration-pdf-form-submission\";s:4:\"name\";s:37:\"User Registration PDF Form Submission\";s:5:\"image\";s:55:\"extensions-json/sections/images/pdf-form-submission.png\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:217:\"PDF Form Submission addon allows to export registration form data in pdf form. PDF are great way to record, print and share with your team members. Automatically attachs the pdf to emails send to your users and admin.\";s:4:\"link\";s:164:\"https://wpuserregistration.com/features/pdf-form-submission/?utm_source=addons-page&utm_medium=banner&utm_campaign=ur-upgrade-to-pro&utm_content=pdf-form-submission\";s:4:\"plan\";a:3:{i:0;s:8:\"personal\";i:1;s:4:\"plus\";i:2;s:12:\"professional\";}}i:1